3⋅\left(\dfrac{1}{3}+π+r^2+h\right)=\left(3\cdot\dfrac{1}{3}+3\cdot π+3\cdot r^2+3\cdot h\right)
3⋅\left(\dfrac{1}{3}πr^2 h\right)=\left(3⋅\dfrac{1}{3}\right)πr^2 h=πr^2 h
